ent-RMCMarineUniformDressGeneral-name = marine general dress blues uniform
ent-RMCMarineUniformDressGeneral-desc = The undershirt and trousers of the legendary Marine dress blues, virtually unchanged since the 19th century. This variant features black trousers and a large Blood Stripe, worn by general officers.

ent-RMCMarineUniformDressSenior-name = marine senior dress blues uniform
ent-RMCMarineUniformDressSenior-desc = The undershirt and trousers of the legendary Marine dress blues, virtually unchanged since the 19th century. This variant features the iconic Blood Stripe, worn by NCOs and officers.

ent-RMCMarineUniformDressEnlisted-name = marine enlisted dress blues uniform
ent-RMCMarineUniformDressEnlisted-desc = The undershirt and trousers of the legendary Marine dress blues, virtually unchanged since the 19th century. This unadorned variant is for enlisted personnel, E-1 thru E-3.

